<concept id="CMD_ai_circtan">
   <title>AI_CIRCTAN Command</title>
   <shortdesc>Creates a tangent circle.</shortdesc>
   <conbody>
      <p>Create a circle tangent to three entities that can include lines, polyline segments, polyarcs, circles, arcs, xlines or rays.</p>
      <fig id="fig_zsh_cxp_x4b"><!--Insert License Level--></fig>
