      </fig>
      <p><!--Alias:--></p>
      <fig id="fig_wpn_d2q_x4b">
         <image href="https://static.bricsys.com/help/en_US/CMD_AICIRCTAN_01_V21.png" id="image_zft_22q_x4b" scope="external" />
      </fig>
      <section id="section_rr5_g2q_x4b">
         <title>Methods to create a tangent circle </title>
         <p>There is one method to begin creating a circle with three tangents:</p>
         <ul id="ul_bry_g2q_x4b">
            <li>Enter tangent spec </li>
         </ul>
         <p>
            <dl>
               <dlentry>
                  <dt>Enter Tangent spec</dt>
                  <dd>Begin creating a circle by selecting a tangent point on the first entity then: </dd>
               </dlentry>
               <dlentry>
                  <dt outputclass="indent1">Enter second Tangent spec</dt>
                  <dd outputclass="indent1">Select a tangent point on the second entity.</dd>
               </dlentry>
               <dlentry>
                  <dt outputclass="indent1">Enter third Tangent spec</dt>
                  <dd outputclass="indent1">Select a tangent point on the third entity.</dd>
               </dlentry>
            </dl>
         </p>
      </section>
